NOTICE OF CLAIM OF LIEN-
HOMEOWNERS ASSESSMENT
Notice is hereby given that
COMSTOCK PARK HOMEOWNERS' ASSOCIATION
a Nevada non-profit corporation, hereinafter called Association, formed to provide the maintenance, preservation,
and architectural control of the residence lots and common area of the Association homeowners in the County of
Nye, State of Nevada, AND PURSUANT TO THE PROVISIONS OF THE NEVADA REVISED STATUTES,
claims a lien upon the real property and buildings, improvements or structures thereon described as follows:
Lot
184
Block
16
_of
CALVADA VALLEY UNIT NO. 8A
as shown on the map thereof recorded _April 5, 1971_ in the Office of the County Recorder of Nye County,
State of Nevada Under Document No. 23255 . Parcel No .: 039-371-04.
Commonly known as: 101 W. Queenstar Street, Pahrump NY 89048
And that the whole of said real estate upon which the buildings are situated is reasonably necessary for the
convenient use and occupancy of said buildings.
That - RUBEN DARIO PRESA and LILLIAN JEANNETTE PRESA. is/are the name (s) of the owner (s) and
reputed owner (s) of said real property and improvements herein above described.
That the prorata assessment which shall constitute a lien against the above described property amounts to $336.00
per year as provided in the DECLARATION OF COVENANTS, CONDITIONS, and RESTRICTIONS which
were recorded on _September 9, 1994, in File No. _ 359149, and all AMENDMENTS and ANNEXATIONS et.
seq ., of Official Records of Nye County, Nevada, at Page _n/a , and which have been supplied to and agreed to
by said owner and reputed owner. That the Association had made demand for payment of the total amount due
and owing, but said sum has not been paid.
THAT THE AMOUNT OWING AND UNPAID TOTALS _$395.38
as of
12/28/2021 ___ and
INCREASES each year at a rate of $ _ 136.00 __ per year, plus LATE CHARGES at the rate of $ 10.00 per
month, PLUS INTEREST at the rate of _5.25% per annum, PLUS ATTORNEY FEES and the FLES of the
AGENT FOR THE MANAGEMENT BODY incurred in connection with preparation, recording, and
foreclosure of this lien,
COMSTOCK PARK HOMEOWNERS' ASSOCIATION
BY:
Michael W. Randolph, Designated Agent
NOTARY SEE ATTACHED EXHIBIT "A"
